dm-scripts README

dm-scripts is an archive of various shell scripts especially useful for 
system administrators and webmasters. All scripts depend on the Bash shell 
and other standard GNU commands. Each script has an -h flag for
usage explanation. The home of the dm-scripts project is:
http://www.comp.eonworks.com


REQUIREMENTS

Bash 2.x or higher; standard GNU commands. Some scripts use commands that
are less common. In such case the required command name is listed when
invoking the script with the -h flag.

Problems and feedback are welcome at author's email: dm@eonworks.com